{"tid":1952813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一名滯留秘魯港人同意TVB引述面書內容後否認授權 TVB表遺憾　","createTime":"2020-03-31T23:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T09:01:08.000Z","uid":133680,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9ae2de61d9a349166cf1c9e9e2e1775f9ae2fc79","tid":1952813,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T23:25:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5e835c5a335d1996570796a4/%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E6%BB%AF%E7%95%99%E7%A7%98%E9%AD%AF%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%B0%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E9%9D%A2%E6%9B%B8%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%E5%BE%8C%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A-%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%B0%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5e835c5a335d1996570796a4%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25BB%25AF%25E7%2595%2599%25E7%25A7%2598%25E9%25AD%25AF%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%258E%2588%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2581%25BA%25E6%2586%25BE&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=793f6d39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5e835c5a335d1996570796a4/%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E6%BB%AF%E7%95%99%E7%A7%98%E9%AD%AF%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%B0%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E9%9D%A2%E6%9B%B8%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%E5%BE%8C%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A-%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%B0%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE</a><br />\n本台星期日報道過，有港人因疫情滯留在秘魯。<br />\n<br />\n該名港人住的秘魯旅館因有兩人確診，旅館被封鎖一至三個月。她在「面書」Facebook上說，有時只獲分配麥皮及麵包做晚餐，要靠在附近仍可出入的港人購買食物。本台按她所講報道。<br />\n<br />\n不過，該名港人今日在社交網站指，未有接受本台訪問，及授權本台取用面書材料。<br />\n<br />\n本台鄭重澄清，她所講的並非實情，本台記者是在星期日下午在社交平台與她聯絡，問她是否能引用她在面書寫的內容，獲對方回應只要註明出處就可以使用。在聯絡的過程中，有徵詢過並獲對方同意，因此本台對她的說法深表遺憾。"},{"pid":"389066f4f0f12ce9aa70b91055c6e06ee8911403","tid":1952813,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T23:33:26.000Z","msg":"I<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02eb6285a3893b0f38ea9c011fad9f594c33cfb","tid":1952813,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T23:40:59.000Z","msg":"搞乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8f444194d6b7fce5df2ab58838e70fc7723055","tid":1952813,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T00:18:04.000Z","msg":"cctvb 侵犯版權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8645d149995c1b974cb1fbe1b7420e83537f36a0","tid":1952813,"uid":350216,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T00:25:06.000Z","msg":"CCTVB既tone越黎越有支那神韻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚴正抗議，強烈譴責，表示遺憾"},{"pid":"2e20342e2f43b9a6bd0faf0c194871b6e3ce290c","tid":1952813,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T00:51:09.000Z","msg":"無圖無真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8326dc9bf59add49a0423056f89a45d1bd687f31","tid":1952813,"uid":13664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T01:44:23.000Z","msg":"柒咗啦！唉。。。"},{"pid":"fdafdb883de1b719e34ba3d5b635cb2a67b1fb6e","tid":1952813,"uid":169529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T01:50:05.000Z","msg":"對話圖都無講經？"},{"pid":"5dd757e2f572d5b315a97f90fabb0c275ccdbe7d","tid":1952813,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T04:10:53.000Z","msg":"廣播事務管理局（廣管局）：未有收到相關投訴"},{"pid":"04e1fc060a1391cbd99071edf126fcd0907fb89e","tid":1952813,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T04:35:31.000Z","msg":"tvb cap埋圖話秘魯港女講大話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1952460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1952460</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論